\pard\f0\fs28  ({\b a}) Subsp. {\b speculum}: Stem not more than 35 cm. Inflorescence 2- to 10-flowered. Inner perianth-segments dark purple. Middle lobe of labellum orbicular-triangular or suborbicular; speculum with wide, yellow margin, the marginal hairs brown or blackish-purple.{\i  Throughout the range of the species}.
